trans-unit.source: A composite activity that contains a collection of event handlers.
trans-unit.target: En sammansatt aktivitet som innehåller en samling händelsehanterare.

trans-unit.source: It is typically used where a collection of events must be handled.
trans-unit.target: Normalt används där en samling av händelser som ska hanteras.

trans-unit.source: Each event is handled by one <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity"></xref>, which is part of EventHandlersActivity.
trans-unit.target: Varje händelsen hanterats av en <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity"> </xref>, vilket är en del av EventHandlersActivity.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The EventHandlersActivity activity holds a set of <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity> classes, for use by the associated <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Aktiviteten EventHandlersActivity innehåller en uppsättning <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity>klasser för användning av den associerade <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity>

trans-unit.source: An EventHandlersActivity activity can only be associated with an <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventHandlingScopeActivity>.
trans-unit.target: En EventHandlersActivity aktivitet kan bara associeras med en <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventHandlingScopeActivity>.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.EventHandlingScopeActivity>

trans-unit.source: The EventHandlersActivity activity is a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, meaning the EventHandlersActivity activity can contain other activities.
trans-unit.target: Aktiviteten EventHandlersActivity är en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, vilket innebär att aktiviteten EventHandlersActivity kan innehålla andra aktiviteter.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventHandlersActivity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventHandlersActivity"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventHandlersActivity"></xref> class by using the name of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventHandlersActivity"> </xref> klassen med namnet på aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: The user-defined name of the activity.

The currently executing instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Instansen som körs för närvarande av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventDrivenActivity"> </xref>.
